transcript:
Customer: Jya vyakti shi apan call kelela aahe, ti sadhya
Customer: Hello. Hello.
Executive: Ha, sir, ji, uh, Dayan Marketing Services se baat kar raha hu main.
Customer: Ha, boliye kaun?
Executive: Sir, good afternoon. Main Sanjay baat kar raha tha head office IndiaMART Noida se branch se.
Customer: Ha, boliye sir.
Executive: Actually sir, ye profile jo aapka IndiaMART pe chal raha hai, ye Noida head office IndiaMART se meri team hi dekhti hai yaha se. Jaise Rabi Shah hai aapke account manager.
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Awaz aa rahi hai aapko meri?
Customer: Ha, ha, aa rahi hai, boliye.
Executive: Ji, sir, abhi na aapka main dekh pa raha hu call aaya hai customer care number pe. So main verify agar aapke mera to ye hai ki mera jo website usme aapne list kar rakha hai na IndiaMART pe to maine just apni website open kiya to usme established year 2007 bata raha hai jabki mera 1996 hai.
Executive: Just hold on sir, line pe rahiye.
Customer: Ha.
Customer: Maine unko photo bhi bheji hai.
Executive: Hmm. Koi dikkat nahi, main dekh raha hu sir.
Customer: Mileage nahi aa rahi hai acche.
Executive: Ek cheez mujhe confirm karaiye sir, established year aap bata rahe ho, right?
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Ye about us me bata rahe ho kya?
Customer: Ha, about us. Line pe rahiye Abishan, Abishan ko aapne bheja hai photo bheji kya?
Customer: Ha, bheji hai maine unko WhatsApp pe. Line pe rahiye.
Executive: Establishment 2000. Okay, okay, okay, okay.
Executive: Okay.
Executive: 1996 hai aapka, right, established?
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Shree, ek baar line pe rahiye, main isko correct kar deta hu ispe. Ha, thoda desktop mat open karna.
Executive: Hold on sir, main kar raha hu, line pe rahiye. Abishan, ha sir. Ye raha Dayan Marketing ke andar send hai aapko wo karaya na. Screenshot bheja hai. Dikhao.
Customer: Sir, ek call aa rahi hai, chalu rakhiye.
Executive: Ji, ji, ji.
